{"tid":1962194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"終審法院拒絕批出「七黑狗」中5隻黑狗上訴許可申請","createTime":"2020-04-07T10:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T10:17:54.000Z","uid":326897,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"70b79840d37b60f0155c41464e32c50467870d6c","tid":1962194,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:04:15.000Z","msg":"終審法院拒絕批出「七警案」5名警員上訴許可申請<br />\n2020-04-07 HKT 11:23<br />\n <br />\n終審法院3名法官拒絕批准「七警案」中5名警員的上訴許可申請。<br />\n<br />\n7名警員2014年佔領運動期間，在金鐘襲擊時任公民黨成員曾健超，他們在2017年被裁定襲擊致造成身體傷害罪成，全部人被判監2年。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭早前裁定當中2名警員上訴得直，獲撤銷定罪及刑期，另外5名警員定罪上訴被駁回，但刑期分別獲減至15個月至18個月不等，這5名警員之後向終審法院申請上訴許可。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519292-20200407.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519292-20200407.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYs4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=8b1ae05a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519292-20200407.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e817e528\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519292-20200407.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5隻黑狗要去做保安啦</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"840d424b284aaf8a2ab2cf886beba8bb62c76709","tid":1962194,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:08:34.000Z","msg":"有案底申請唔到保安證 , 所以坐足左都堅持上訴想洗底<br />\n<br />\n不過5年後警務署長有權照批"},{"pid":"10827b58635407104fee2bb9eed9c5a9af1a5e9f","tid":1962194,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:11:48.000Z","msg":"出番來做黑社會囉，反正做既野都一樣"},{"pid":"0981bb72b691d5d27e1a513512a8d9c045fcd64d","tid":1962194,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70b79840d37b60f0155c41464e32c50467870d6c","tid":1962194,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim